          "evidence_text_excerpt": "ffered by The Toronto-Dominion Bank. Savings Accounts offered by TD\nMortgage Corporation, except in British Columbia or Yukon, which are offered by TD Pacific Mortgage Corporation. All Savings Accounts are guaranteed by\nThe Toronto-Dominion Bank. Any accounts opened at Canada Trust prior to conversion to TD Canada Trust are issued by The Canada Trust Company. TD\nMortgage Corporation and TD Pacific Mortgage Corporation are loan companies governed by the Trust and Loan Companies Act of Canada , and member\ninstitutions of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation. The Canada Trust Company is a trust company governed by the Trust and Loan Companies Act of\nCanada, and a member institution of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation.\nTo compare bank account options, access the FCAC Account Selector Tool at www.fcac-acfc.gc.ca/Eng/resources/toolsCalculators/Pages/BankingT-OutilsIn.aspx\n.\n\u00ae The",
